    <div id="status-tab" class="content-tab-panel">
            <p><div class="content_para"><p>This is the current release of the guideline.</p>
<p>This guideline updates a previous version: National Collaborating Centre for Chronic Conditions. Tuberculosis. Clinical diagnosis and management of tuberculosis, and measures for its prevention and control. London (UK): National Institute for Health and Clinical Excellence (NICE); 2011 Mar. 64 p. (Clinical guideline; no. 117).</p>
<p>This guideline meets NGC's 2013 (revised) inclusion criteria.</p></div></p>
