                    <h4>UMLS Concepts <a href="/web/20180713022442/https://www.guideline.gov/help-and-about/search-browse/umls-concepts" class="what-is">(what is this?)</a></h4>
                <div class="field">
                    <h5 class="field-label">ICD9CM</h5>
                    <div class="field-content">
<a href="/web/20180713022442/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0011923&amp;fLockTerm=Diagnostic+imaging%2c+not+elsewhere+classified">Diagnostic imaging, not elsewhere classified</a>
 (88.90), <a href="/web/20180713022442/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0017134&amp;fLockTerm=Gastric+lavage">Gastric lavage</a>
 (96.33), <a href="/web/20180713022442/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0374973&amp;fLockTerm=Genitourinary+tuberculosis%2c+unspecified%2c+unspecified">Genitourinary tuberculosis, unspecified, unspecified</a>
 (016.90), <a href="/web/20180713022442/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0041321&amp;fLockTerm=Miliary+tuberculosis%2c+unspecified%2c+unspecified">Miliary tuberculosis, unspecified, unspecified</a>
 (018.90), <a href="/web/20180713022442/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0374962&amp;fLockTerm=Other+tuberculosis+of+intestines%2c+peritoneum%2c+and+mesenteric+glands%2c+unspecified">Other tuberculosis of intestines, peritoneum, and mesenteric glands, unspecified</a>
 (014.80), <a href="/web/20180713022442/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C1812612&amp;fLockTerm=Primary+tuberculous+infection%2c+unspecified">Primary tuberculous infection, unspecified</a>
 (010.00), <a href="/web/20180713022442/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0041327&amp;fLockTerm=Pulmonary+tuberculosis%2c+unspecified%2c+unspecified">Pulmonary tuberculosis, unspecified, unspecified</a>
 (011.90), <a href="/web/20180713022442/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0152861&amp;fLockTerm=Tuberculosis+of+peripheral+lymph+nodes%2c+unspecified">Tuberculosis of peripheral lymph nodes, unspecified</a>
 (017.20), <a href="/web/20180713022442/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0374974&amp;fLockTerm=Tuberculosis+of+skin+and+subcutaneous+cellular+tissue%2c+unspecified">Tuberculosis of skin and subcutaneous cellular tissue, unspecified</a>
 (017.00), <a href="/web/20180713022442/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0041330&amp;fLockTerm=Tuberculosis+of+vertebral+column%2c+unspecified">Tuberculosis of vertebral column, unspecified</a>
 (015.00), <a href="/web/20180713022442/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0374955&amp;fLockTerm=Tuberculous+laryngitis%2c+unspecified">Tuberculous laryngitis, unspecified</a>
 (012.30), <a href="/web/20180713022442/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0041326&amp;fLockTerm=Tuberculous+pleurisy%2c+unspecified">Tuberculous pleurisy, unspecified</a>
 (012.00), <a href="/web/20180713022442/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0275904&amp;fLockTerm=Unspecified+tuberculosis+of+central+nervous+system%2c+unspecified">Unspecified tuberculosis of central nervous system, unspecified</a>
 (013.90)                    </div>
